ras/7c5fde71f6d48d591badb5aedfffbcb9.poster.avif?t=1772354630\" width=780 height=520 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186770/extras/7c5fde71f6d48d591badb5aedfffbcb9.webm?t=1772354630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186770/extras/7c5fde71f6d48d591badb5aedfffbcb9.mp4?t=1772354630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>to find out the truth and to finish the mission.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>I believe the escape room genre is a perfect fit for VR, which is why I continue to create immersive escape room games. I hope you have as much fun playing this game as I had developing it. Your feedback is always welcome. Enjoy!</strong></p>",
